reviewText: Bought it for nothing I can't watch it

I purchased this dvd off of some Japanese site. It took literally months to get to me, but it was worth the wright, it is probably one of  the best looking dvds in my collection. As far as the movie it is awesome, a little more violent then most g movies but definitly a gem in the whole daikaiju genre. I'm glad I own this.

I bought biollante and this movie for less than 20 dollars off of ebay the movies are the real ones the chinese versions do include english subs this one looks the best out of the two the other being in full screen.
